title: .net Magazine UK July 2012
description:
.net Magazine UK July 2012

.Net Magazine is a great modern magazine which provides a complete guide 
to the internet. It aims to help businesses get better established and 
is ideal for businesses looking to get into the wider internet community 
and drive sales to your site or service. Net magazine aims to equip 
readers with the knowledge to get more confident when using the internet 
as well as being a useful tool for web designers who are already 
established in the sector.

English | 148 pages | HQ PDF | 104.00 Mb
